title: Vitality Documentary 2014
description:
In January 2014 WELL.ORG released an exciting journey into the nature of what true health is and how we can attain it individually. The problems of the broken medical system revolve around trying to constantly fix problems that emerge from how we live.

Medical experts from around the world weigh in as we explore the simple solutions that can drastically change our relationships with our bodies.

Vitality is more than merely the absence of disease, it means being able to live life fully and thrive in the world.

If you like this video BE SURE AND CHECK OUT the WELL.ORG NEW VIDEO called ORIGINS Documentary. You can see it on YouTube and download it from my uploaded files.

Enjoy learning the Truths of Life.
